aboutThisItem: Bourjois Healthy Mix 2-in-1 Serum Concealer seamlessly combines the benefits of a high-coverage concealer with the revitalizing effects of an eye serum.
It instantly refreshes, brightens, and lifts the under-eye area for a more awake and youthful look.
